            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Vibio <lb n="3"/>Vibiaes <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erto</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Iusto <lb n="5"/>qui vixit an<lb break="no" n="6"/>nos XLVIIII me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>XI et Camplan<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="8"/>Afrodite praepo<lb break="no" n="9"/>sitis posuit <note>sic</note> <lb n="10"/>Fortio pedise<lb break="no" n="11"/>cus <note>sic</note> et Chrysostomus <lb n="12"/>pedisecus <note>sic</note> <lb n="13"/>ut famuli potuimus tibe <note>sic</note> digno me<lb break="no" n="14"/>renti ho<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>c</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>titulo</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> posuimus <expan><abbr>tuo</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="15"/>comitatus <note>sic</note> honorem cot <note>sic</note> fue<lb break="no" n="16"/>rit in nos tu<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> tantus amor <lb n="17"/>tu nobis ut genitor tantus pie<lb break="no" n="18"/>tate fuisti cot <note>sic</note> facit et nos fa<lb break="no" n="19"/>ta finemque rogare nec pre<lb break="no" n="20"/>cibus adsunt set <note>sic</note> cruciant d<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>u</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="21"/>tius viduatos vitaes <note>sic</note> honore <lb n="22"/>Chromati spiri<lb break="no" n="23"/>tus incompara<lb break="no" n="24"/>&amp;lt;b=R&amp;gt;ilis 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Stele ist in 2 Teile gebrochen. AE 1931, Sabbadini: Text ab Z. 13 nicht wiedergegeben. Sabbadini: keine Zeilentrenner angegeben. AE 1933: ab Z. 13 keine Zeilentrenner angegeben. (B): AE 1931: Z. 1/2: D. T. Vibio M.; Bernini, AE 1931: Z. 5: XLVIII men.; Z. 6: XI e Camplane; Sabbadini: Z. 9: posuit nicht angegeben; Bernini, AE 1931: Z. 11: Chrisostomus; Bernini: Z. 16: tuus; Bernini: Z. 23/24: incompa/rabilis; Aurigemma, AE 1983, Niedermann: Z. 23/24: incompara/bilis.</p>
            </div>
